{"tid":940814,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"彭博：中國製造2025擬緩10年","createTime":"2018-12-14T08:32:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-24T09:12:22.000Z","uid":141151,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"555812c3466e310927baa6ba4f9b05013039a84e","tid":940814,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"彭博：中國製造2025擬緩10年<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20181214/s00013/1544725545302/%e5%bd%ad%e5%8d%9a-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%a3%bd%e9%80%a02025%e6%93%ac%e7%b7%a910%e5%b9%b4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20181214%2Fs00013%2F1544725545302%2F%25e5%25bd%25ad%25e5%258d%259a-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25a3%25bd%25e9%2580%25a02025%25e6%2593%25ac%25e7%25b7%25a910%25e5%25b9%25b4&d=fPCWDw3FhU9n97cnZSL7WP755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=299d56b2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%2Farticle%2F20181214%2Fs00013%2F1544725545302%2F%25e5%25bd%25ad%25e5%258d%259a-%25e4%25b8%25ad%25e5%259c%258b%25e8%25a3%25bd%25e9%2580%25a02025%25e6%2593%25ac%25e7%25b7%25a910%25e5%25b9%25b4&h=37d01561\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/pns/%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b/article/20181214/s00013/1544725545302/%e5%bd%ad%e5%8d%9a-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e8%a3%bd%e9%80%a02025%e6%93%ac%e7%b7%a910%e5%b9%b4</a><br />\n<br />\n【明報專訊】彭博社報道，北京正考慮將受爭議的產業政策「中國製造2025」中某些方面推遲10年至2035年，但具體的修訂方案仍待決定，亦未知是否已經傳達給特朗普政府。此外，路透社稱中國已經購買150噸美國大豆，明年1至3月付運。<br />\n<br />\n路透：華購150噸美國大豆 明年初付運<br />\n<br />\n另據路透社報道，中國國營企業購入至少50萬噸大豆，是自中美貿易戰以來首次。據交易商估計，該批大豆的總價格超過1.8億美元（約14億港元）。彭博社則稱，訂單總量是150至200噸。中國商務部發言人高峰昨日回應稱，「大豆一直是中國進口美國的重要商品，中國國內對此有巨大的市場需求」，但他沒有提供具體數額，僅表示「如果有進一步的細節，我會進一步通告」，至於中美官員下一步磋商，高峰稱「目前雙方正在保持密切聯繫。中方歡迎美方來華開展磋商，也對赴美溝通持開放態度」。"},{"pid":"219f1bc4a543a8d5a6d777f22ceef44fa6926a4b","tid":940814,"uid":37375,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:33:31.000Z","msg":"2035 習近平都死埋"},{"pid":"ae28ad24fc391f7dbee0c80b370ab0bf7c4d3644","tid":940814,"uid":26752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:33:47.000Z","msg":"2035<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21624174ea607e0410e5cac40a72ac171feeecd3","tid":940814,"uid":26752,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"靈芝孢子<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eccd98e5da3000f30ed986b1b868c6232bc8844","tid":940814,"uid":60150,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:36:34.000Z","msg":"中國製造2035<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f306f2075e99a01217a49f9d5ef65bce50c80e88","tid":940814,"uid":117276,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:37:36.000Z","msg":"支那以為自己可以捱到2035<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"60df575ba64777e3debfed9c3b0db193a7b9bc97","tid":940814,"uid":163350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:39:30.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"289a46ed40a3a38d67f7ad8fc6615ca5e382e8bd","tid":940814,"uid":45518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:40:34.000Z","msg":"fake news?"},{"pid":"d71a113e42e01cd085be47bc5b05ef267ffc8152","tid":940814,"uid":24788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-14T08:52:08.000Z","msg":"弱智先會公開呢d政策"},{"pid":"04be5e1265c66503571400fef257ea03a6e168c5","tid":940814,"uid":36901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-1